Aar taanga paar taanga

Wich taalaam talliyaan

Main peer manaawan challiyaan
I'm going to Make my King my Leader.

Ehde matthe himalay da taaj

I have very powerful Friends & Foes. 
I lead a simple satasfied meaningful life 
& Follow simple two rules. "Never leave a friend & Never leave an enemy." 
& 
"Don't care about what people think cause those who matter don't care & those who don't care- don't matter."
Superbly & hugely Blessed for that. 
 
I have an elephants memory & that's a huge boon cause Since the time I remember, gratefully my request/prayer to Hanuman are just two...........  
That I may NEVER remember a good or favour done by me for someone/anyone - NEVER. 
& 
that i may NEVER forget a good or favour done for me by someone/anyone.....NEVER. 
& 
That I may never leave a friend. &
Never leave an enemy. 

These have been my only prayers/ request/begging to my dear friend - Hanuman.

Blessed Beyond Expectations & Deserving!!!

Ever Grateful, Thankful, Beholden, Obligated, Indebted, In Gratitude, to My Family, Indian Army, Cavalry & The Horse. 

Indebted & Obligated to them for life. Whatever I am today is only thanks to the blessings of Hanuman & all of them.
